user.biography: James Beard Nominee, 2x IACP nominee, cook, host, author, My cookbook, MI COCINA, comes out Spring ‘22

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Rick Martinez in Mazatlán, Sinaloa. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: All of my favorite things. Grilled shrimp, mango, pineapple and lime.

✨ ¡TORTAS AHOGADAS! ✨ This episode reignited my love of baking bread! But now, especially birote salado! Lots of love to my amazing crew who made this episode so absolutely stunning!  Link in my bio! And as always, lots of love to @bingingwithbabish for making this possible! .  Director - @seabassfilms 
Camera B - @juanchvz98 
Producer - @gerry.cruz 
Animation - @diegomedrano 
Editing - @seabasortega and @bradacash

node.text: I’m super excited to announce that I am partnering with OXO and will be one of their Chefs in Residence. OXO Chefs in Residence is a brand-new program pairing culinary experts with OXO's innovative tools to bring virtual inspiration to home cooks everywhere. Over the next few months, I'll share the things that excite me in the kitchen and the tools I love and use every day. Stay tuned here and @oxo for my exclusive recipes and tips. **Have a burning kitchen question? Check out @oxo Instagram stories September 7 - 10, and I'll help answer! #ad #oxobetter

node.text: We are making a podcast. A food podcast. And we want your help! Tell us your food probs. Big or small. We want to solve all your food conundrums. Call 833433 FOOD and tell us your food problems! We are here to help! 😘 we are standing by... no dms please! 🙏🏾

node.text: BIRRIA episode 2 of Pruébalo is up! There is not a word to capture how incredibly grateful I am to be working with such talented people. @seabasortega @juanchvz98 @gerry.cruz @diegomedrano @bradacash WE DID IT! You guys are amazing. And HUGE thank you to @the_goat_mafia for letting us tell this story! Link to the video is in my profile!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rick Martinez on July 10, 2021 tagging @hilarycadigan, @seabasortega, @juanchvz98, @gerry.cruz, and @bingingwithbabish. May be an image of 1 person, ocean, sky and text.

node.text: I AM BEYOND EXCITED! My new show PRUÉBALO is up and I am so proud, so grateful and so happy to be able to show everyone how incredibly beautiful Mexico, Mexicans and the food we eat really is. Huge thank you to @bingingwithbabish for letting me tell this story. 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾 And to @seabasortega @seabassfilms for your INSANELY GORGEOUS CINEMATOGRAPHY!!! 😍😍😍 And to @gerry.cruz for helping us develop the stories we are going to share. And to @juanchvz98 for your amazing camerawork! I am so full of love atm. Link to the show in my profile!
